                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section1Title") I. General Provisions
                                    ol
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section1Point1") The Privacy Policy defines how personal data of Users necessary for the provision of services electronically via the website (hereinafter: the Service) is collected, processed and stored.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section1Point2") The Service collects only personal data necessary for the provision and development of services offered therein.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section1Point3") Personal data collected through the Service is processed in accordance with Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016 on the protection of natural persons with regard to the processing of personal data and on the free movement of such data, and repealing Directive 95/46/EC (General Data Protection Regulation, hereinafter GDPR) and the Act on the Protection of Personal Data of 10 May 2018.

                            // II. Administrator danych
                            .card.overflow-hidden.shadow.rounded-4.border-0.mb-5
                                .card-body.p-5
                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section2Title") II. Data Controller
                                    p(data-i18n="section2Content") The controller of personal data collected through the Service is Nexi8 Ali Bińkowska, Tax ID: 9820253147, email address: kontakt @ alibinkowska.co (hereinafter: the Controller).

                            // III. Cel zbierania danych osobowych
                            .card.overflow-hidden.shadow.rounded-4.border-0.mb-5
                                .card-body.p-5
                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section3Title") III. Purpose of Collecting Personal Data
                                    ol
                                        li.mb-3
                                            span(data-i18n="section3Point1Intro") Personal data is used for the purpose of:
                                            ul.mt-2
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point1Item1") communicating with the User via the contact form,
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point1Item2") responding to inquiries sent through the contact form,
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point1Item3") promoting the Controller's offer,
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point1Item4") marketing, remarketing, affiliation,
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point1Item5") personalizing the Service for Users,
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point1Item6") analytical and statistical activities.

                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section3Point2") Data collected through the contact form includes: name, email address, phone number (optional), and message content. This data is processed solely for the purpose of responding to the inquiry and possible further communication with the User.
                                        li.mb-3
                                            span(data-i18n="section3Point3Intro") The legal basis for processing personal data is:
                                            ul.mt-2
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point3Item1") Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (performance of a contract) - in the case of service provision,
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point3Item2") Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest) - in the case of communication via the contact form, where the controller has a legitimate interest in responding to the inquiry,
                                                li(data-i18n="section3Point3Item3") Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR (consent) - in the case of marketing activities requiring consent.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section3Point4") Providing data is voluntary but necessary to enter into a contract or use other functionalities of the Service, including receiving a response to an inquiry sent through the contact form.

