                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section5Title") V. Period of Processing Personal Data
                                    p.mb-3(data-i18n="section5Intro") Users' personal data will be processed for a period of:
                                    ul
                                        li(data-i18n="section5Point1") when the basis for data processing is the performance of a contract - until the expiry of claims after its performance,
                                        li(data-i18n="section5Point2") when the basis for data processing is consent - until its withdrawal, and after withdrawal of consent until the expiry of claims,
                                        li(data-i18n="section5Point3") in the case of data from the contact form - for the period necessary to provide a response and for the period of expiry of any claims.
                                    p.mt-3(data-i18n="section5Conclusion") In both cases, the limitation period is 6 years, and for claims for periodic benefits and claims related to business activity - 3 years (unless a special provision states otherwise).

                            // VI. Udostępnianie danych osobowych
                            .card.overflow-hidden.shadow.rounded-4.border-0.mb-5
                                .card-body.p-5
                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section6Title") VI. Sharing Personal Data
                                    ol
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section6Point1") Users' personal data may be transferred to: entities affiliated with the Controller, its subcontractors, entities cooperating with the Controller, e.g. hosting companies, law firms.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section6Point2") Users' personal data will not be transferred outside the European Economic Area (EEA).

                            // VII. Prawa Użytkowników
                            .card.overflow-hidden.shadow.rounded-4.border-0.mb-5
                                .card-body.p-5
                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section7Title") VII. Users' Rights
                                    ol
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section7Point1") The User of the Service has the right to: access the content of their personal data, rectify it, delete it, restrict processing, transfer it, object to processing, withdraw consent at any time (which does not affect the lawfulness of processing carried out on the basis of consent before its withdrawal).
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section7Point2") A notice of the User exercising a right resulting from the mentioned rights should be sent to the address kontakt @ alibinkowska.co
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section7Point3") The Controller fulfills or refuses to fulfill the request immediately - at most within one month of receiving it.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section7Point4") The User has the right to lodge a complaint with the President of the Personal Data Protection Office if they believe that the processing violates their rights and freedoms (GDPR).

                            // VIII. Pliki cookies
                            .card.overflow-hidden.shadow.rounded-4.border-0.mb-5
                                .card-body.p-5
                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section8Title") VIII. Cookies
                                    ol
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section8Point1") The Service collects information using cookies - session, permanent and third-party cookies.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section8Point2") Collecting cookies supports the proper provision of services in the Service and serves statistical purposes.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section8Point3") The User can determine the scope of access of cookies to their device in the browser settings.

                            // IX. Zautomatyzowane podejmowanie decyzji i profilowanie
                            .card.overflow-hidden.shadow.rounded-4.border-0.mb-5
                                .card-body.p-5
                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section9Title") IX. Automated Decision-Making and Profiling
                                    ol
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section9Point1") Users' data may not be processed in an automated manner such that any decisions could be made about them as a result.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section9Point2") Users' data may be profiled for the purpose of adjusting content and personalizing the offer after they have given their consent.

                            // X. Postanowienia końcowe
                            .card.overflow-hidden.shadow.rounded-4.border-0.mb-5
                                .card-body.p-5
                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.text-primary(data-i18n="section10Title") X. Final Provisions
                                    ol
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section10Point1") The Controller has the right to introduce changes to the Privacy Policy, whereby Users' rights will not be limited.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section10Point2") Information about introduced changes will appear in the form of a message available in the Service.
                                        li.mb-3(data-i18n="section10Point3") In matters not regulated in this Privacy Policy, the provisions of the GDPR and provisions of Polish law shall apply.

